sections.heading: Board, defined.Prior to July 1, 2026, board means the Board of Advanced Practice Registered Nurses
sections.text: Beginning July 1, 2026, board means the Board of Nursing.SourceLaws 1984, LB 761, § 6;Laws 1993, LB 536, § 74;Laws 1999, LB 828, § 161;Laws 2005, LB 256, § 83;R.S.Supp.,2006, § 71-1743;Laws 2007, LB46
